        <h3>Core focus area as Networking Expert</h3>

        <p>The Internet is the basic technology of the Information Age; more than any other technology, networking, and communications have changed how we live, putting the Internet at our fingertips.</p>

        <p>The Networking and Communications areas focus on the architecture and design of data networks, communication systems, computer networks, and Web technologies. The Internet is the best example of interconnected computer networks that use the Internet protocol suite (TCP/IP) to communicate between many data networks, computer networks, and devices. Packet switching, used to group data transmitted over a digital network, is an integral part of this technology.</p>

        <p>As a networking expert, Dr. Lavian focuses on the architecture and design of data networks, communication systems, computer networks, and Web technologies. This includes a deep understanding of the Internet and how it works and the technologies that enable communication and connectivity between different networks and devices.</p>

        <p>Dr. Lavian's practical experience with a range of networking technologies, including ITCP/IP and packet switching, is a testament to his hands-on skills. His expertise extends to designing and implementing network architectures that support various applications and environments, including LANs, WANs, and other types of networks. He also has a proven track record in configuring network devices and services, such as routers, switches, firewalls, and gateways.</p>

        <p>In addition to his technical expertise, Dr. Lavian has experience testing and evaluating networks to ensure they function correctly and meet performance and reliability requirements. This includes experience with various network testing tools and techniques, such as network performance testing, network security testing, and network interoperability testing.</p>

        <p>Dr. Lavian's unwavering focus as a networking expert is on the architecture, design, and implementation of data networks, communication systems, computer networks, and Web technologies. His comprehensive approach and expertise in these areas enable him to assist companies and organizations in designing, implementing, and maintaining networks that cater to their specific needs and requirements.</p>
